# 🚗 Drive By Rihem - Car Rental Website

A modern and responsive car rental website designed for **Drive By Rihem Tunisia**.

This project was developed using pure HTML and CSS as part of a web design and front-end development project.

---

## 📋 Project Overview

Drive By Rihem is a car rental company operating in Tunisia.

This website allows users to:

- Browse available rental vehicles
- View current promotions
- Learn about the company
- Explore available agencies
- Request quotes and reservations
- Access contact information

The website is fully responsive and adapts to desktop, tablet, and mobile devices.

---

## 🎨 Features

### Navigation Bar
- Company logo
- Navigation menu
- User icons

### Hero Section
- Promotional banner
- Online reservation discount offer

### Booking Section
- Pick-up location
- Pick-up date and time
- Drop-off date and time
- Reservation button

### Promotions
- Featured rental vehicles
- Daily pricing information
- Booking buttons

### Services
- Professional service information
- Agency information

### About Us
- Company presentation
- Agency image
- Call-to-action button

### Why Choose Drive By Rihem
- Safe & Insured
- 24/7 Support
- Best Prices

### Footer
- Airport agencies
- City agencies
- Useful links
- Payment methods
- Social media links

---

## 🛠 Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- Font Awesome Icons
- Google Fonts

